About this item

  • Wall Mount Phone Holder: UGREEN smartphone wall holder can give your phone a safe dock while charging. With wide range of application, this wall mount for phone can be used on smooth and even wallpaper, lime wall, tile, stainless steel, glass, wooden and metal surface.（Newly upgraded 3M adhesive, more firmly pasted）
  • Easy Mount: The phone charging holder could be easily attached to your wall with smooth surface, such as ceramic wall, glass wall, Lime wall and wall with wallpaper. Please be kindly noted that it's okay to get it off the wall, but the holder is not reusable any more.
  • Universal Compatibility: UGREEN cell phone wall mount fits for all mobile phones. Note: Make sure the thickness of device with case is within 14mm. Compatible for iPhone 11 12 Pro Max, new iPhone SE 2, iPhone X XR 8 7 Plus 6S 6 5s 5, Samsung Galaxy Note20 S20 Ultra S10 S10e S10+ S9 Plus S8 Note 9 8 S7 S6 Edge S5, LG G7 G8 V40 ThinQ V20 V30 G5 G6, Google Pixel 4 3a 3 2 XL, Nexus 5X 6P 7 6 5, OnePlus 7T 6 5T 3T 5 android phone. Note: This smartphone wall dock cannot be used for tablets or iPad.
  • User Friendly Design: Built-in non-slip pad for stable placement and charging cable organizing for no tangled mess. The phone charge holder is made of ABS plastic, non-toxic, no smell and heat-resisting. Sturdy, durable and environmentally-friendly.
  • What You Get: 1x UGREEN wall mount for cellphone charging.

Product Description

Conveneint Use of UGREEN Phone Holder Wall Mount While Charging

UGREEN wall mount phone holder can give your phone a safe dock while charging. Built-in non-slip pad and charging cable organizing can avoid your phone falling off and tangled mess. It is the perfect storage solution for your smartphone when it is charging.

Features

Easy installation, Not harmful to electronics, Convenience to put the devices when charging.

Compatibility

Compatible with iPhone 12 11 Pro Max, iPhone 12 mini, iPhone XS XR, iPhone X, iPhone 8, 8 Plus, iPhone 7, 6S, 5, Samsung Galaxy S9 S9+ S8 S8 Plus S7 S6, S6 Edge S5, S4, S3, Note 3, Note 4 and more.

Note: Thickness of device with case should be within 14 mm.

Size: 117x69 mm, Material: ABS

Read more

How to Use

This wall phone holder is designed to be attached to the wall. Do please make sure the wall you stick is dry and clean and with a smooth surface.

After you stick this product to your wall, please wait for 24 hours before using it to make sure it sticks firmly.

Please be kindly noted that it's okay to get it off the wall, but the holder is not reusable anymore.

Important Notes

The Plugs and cables just for show, not included.

Intended only for use on smooth, non-textured surfaces.

      HALL OF FAMETOP 50 REVIEWERVINE VOICE
      4.0 out of 5 stars The clean look is marred by the unattractive logo on the front
      Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2017
      Verified Purchase
      About a year ago I bought a phone holder with a similar purpose. That device was made with two separate pieces (so it was adjustable). I didn’t care for it. This one is more like some sunglass clips I have seen in that it is more like a cradle. I would not call it adjustable either; the plastic is too hard to flex to accommodate various phone thicknesses. So it is either going to fit your phone or not and the best way to be sure is to try it, that is especially true if your phone has a case on it. I bought it to use with an iPhone 5SE with a case on it and it fits, but very snugly.

      The holder is mounted to the wall using a non-reusable adhesive disc on the rear which is ingeniously designed to stand off far enough from the holder to provide a place to wrap most charging cables. I say the disc is non-reusable because that is what the seller states. In real-life you can buy round 3M adhesive discs and use two of them to relocate the phone holder as many times as you want.

      I like this case and consider it a good value. It is not lined in any way and that might be a concern as the relatively sharp lip on the front edge could scratch the screen on some phones or break off the buttons on some Android phones.

      When comparing this phone holder I favorably compared it to another brand from Carmilo which sells for the same price. The two look identical. When I looked at the product reviews from that brand the user-supplied photos showed the name Ugreen printed on the holder, so it appears to be the same product being sold as two different brands.

      Speaking of the logo on the holder, when I buy a product based on its style I don’t like to have the seller push their advertising in my face every time I look at it after I have bought and paid for it. I know almost all consumer goods have brand logos on them, and it’s something we have to accept from the major manufacturers, but on a product like this I would much prefer to not have the logo (in Chinese) printed right on the front. Suggestion to the manufacturer – how about printing it on the back plate so it is not visible when the phone is in the holder?

      Since it wasn’t a great fit for my phone I ended up using it on my nightstand table to hold the remote controls for my bedroom fan and space heater, which I want access to while I am in bed. It was a perfect fit for them (and they are much thinner than most cell phones) and since alls well that ends well I actually do like this product.
      Read more

It actually takes the weight of an ipad without issue and would work well for one except it isn't big enough for a case as well, but it's not meant for ipad I don't think. The inside is covered in a sort of felt material so no risk of scratches. I have a slim gel case on my phone but I think it would probably still be ok with a chunkier one. Maybe not a full on otterbox though!

      I have an iPhone 6s but this also fits the 5s and would undoubtedly fit an ipod touch too. Please do a bigger version for ipad in cases!
